      public static Object[] addPuz() throws CustomExeptionClass
      This method prompts the user to input information about a puzzle product and creates an Object array with the information. The information includes the name, brand, price, stock, age, material type, and type.
      Returns:
      Object array with the animal product information.
      Throws:
      CustomExeptionClass - when the price, age or stock input is negative.
